_sText:
This is a Gun Game map.

I am the original designer and creator of this map. Please do not steal it and if you wish to remake it please add otto_man10 to steam and ask em first, and also make sure to include me as the original creator of the map.

This map was originaly made for Trident-Gaming (www.trident-gaming.net), but the Gun Game server has been turned into a war maps server so I decided That I would share it with all of you.

To install, simply drag the folder into your maps folder in cstrike and you will be ready to play when you go in-game!

Hope you enjoy playing on my map ;).
